<keyLead box="[151,1436,574,597]" pageId="5" pageNumber="18">
1. Both glumes shorter than the anthecium. Continental Africa and weedy on 
<collectingCountry box="[1000,1111,574,597]" name="Saint Helena, Ascension and Tristan da Cunha" pageId="5" pageNumber="18">Ascension</collectingCountry>
<emphasis box="[1112,1436,574,597]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="18">
............................. 
