<quantity box="[273,367,990,1013]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="6.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="18" unit="cm" value="8.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="6.0">6–10 cm</quantity>
tall. Panicle 
<quantity box="[509,589,990,1013]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="18" unit="cm" value="1.5" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.0">1–2 cm</quantity>
long, largely hidden in the leaves. Spikelets ca. 
<quantity box="[1113,1176,990,1013]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" pageId="5" pageNumber="18" unit="mm" value="2.0">2 mm</quantity>
long. 
<collectingCountry box="[1245,1432,990,1013]" name="Ascension Island" pageId="5" pageNumber="18">Ascension Island</collectingCountry>
, endemic, endangered 
<emphasis box="[426,1436,1022,1045]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="18">
................................................................................................................................. 
